snippet.title: War in the East 2 || Reveal Interview with Joel Billings / 2by3 Games
snippet.description:
Matrix Games' Operational Director Erik Rutins interviews Joel Billings (2by3 Games) about his new game: War in the East 2
🎮 Wishlist here 👉https://bit.ly/2JJ1RtA

War in the East 2 is the most comprehensive, most realistic, and most advanced wargame modeling Eastern Front warfare in World War.
